Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方 - 我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们的月球突然消失又当如何呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What would happen if our Moon suddenly disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全球性海啸将摧毁世界各地的海岸线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Global tsunamis decimate coastlines around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为海水涌向了太阳的引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as ocean waters surge toward the gravitational pull of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋流变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sea currents shift,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变着气象模式 破坏了食品供应\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}changing weather patterns and destroying food supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终地球自转轴倾角失控\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eventually Earth's axis tilts wildly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变两极为热带丛林\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}turning the poles into tropical jungles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤道成寒冷的不毛之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the equator into frigid wastelands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的物种出现 其它物种则消亡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}New species emerge, while others go extinct.
